node.text:
In this episode we get to meet @sv0888 CEO of @papayatutor. We get to learn about her journey as an immigrant to becoming an entrepreneur and starting a tutoring platform.

Special thanks to our sponsors:
@lumisautomation 

Produced by: @stemedia 

#womenempowerment #wisw #engineeringmemes #interview #entrepreneur #education #empowerment #tutoring

node.title: Engineer to entrepreneur - Starting a tutoring platform
